Package: konenMCBB
Type: Package
Title: College Basketball Data Digestion for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Charlie", "Konen",
      email = "konen2332@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A unified interface for pulling, parsing, and storing college
    basketball data from multiple sources: Bart Torvik (barttorvik.com) for
    advanced team and player efficiency metrics, ESPN for live and historical
    game data (box scores, play-by-play, betting lines, win probability),
    Sports Reference for rosters and player game logs, NCAA.com for
    play-by-play, and Covers.com for injury data. Includes a local flat-file
    ESPN database pipeline and utilities for loading data into PostgreSQL.
